    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Luminescence dating technique, where mineral samples are heated to 400 to 500 degrees Celsius and are measured to determine the release of stored energy in the form of light.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000019801/Hole and Heizer, Prehistoric Archaeology (1977)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Método de datación de objetos calentándolos a 400 hasta 500 grados Celsius o midiendo la liberación de energía almacenada en forma de luz.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Luminescentiemethode om ouderdom vast te stellen door minerale monsters te verwarmen tot een temperatuur tussen de 400 en 500 graden Celsius en vervolgens te meten hoeveel opgeslagen energie er vrijkomt in de vorm van licht.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052378/Winkler Prins Encyclopedie (1990)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>螢光定年法的技術，將礦物樣本加熱至攝氏400到500度以測定以光形式儲存之能量的釋放。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
